        WestCacheItem get(WestCacheOption option,
                  String cacheKey,
                  Callable<WestCacheItem> callable)
        Get the cached item from cache with firstly built.

        The cache implementation should use callable to create cache value when the cache is firstly built.

        Parameters:
        option - westcache settings.
        cacheKey - cache key.
        callable - under callable when cache is first built.
        Returns:
        cache item.
